<i>noun</i>: 허드렛일 [허드렌닐], 허드레 [허드레], 잡무 [잠무], 가사 [가사] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>허드렛일 [허드렌닐]</dt><br>
<dd>chores; miscellaneous work; odd jobs</dd><br>
<dd>중요하지 아니하고 허름한 일.</dd><br>
<dd>A task considered as unimportant and trivial.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>허드레 [허드레]</dt><br>
<dd>odds and ends; miscellaneous items; chores</dd><br>
<dd>중요하지 않고 허름하여 함부로 쓸 수 있는 물건.</dd><br>
<dd>Objects so unimportant and shabby as to be handled roughly.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>잡무 [잠무]</dt><br>
<dd>chores; miscellaneous work; odd jobs</dd><br>
<dd>여러 가지 자질구레한 사무나 일.</dd><br>
<dd>Sundry, trifling business affairs or jobs.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>가사 [가사]</dt><br>
<dd>housework; chores</dd><br>
<dd>집안 살림살이에 관한 일.</dd><br>
<dd>Activities related to homemaking.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>